#. type: Title ==
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/performance-measure.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "JVM flags for benchmarking"
msgstr "用于基准测试的 JVM 参数"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/performance-measure.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The benchmark scripts apply these JVM flags when running the application under test:"
msgstr "基准测试脚本在运行被测应用程序时会应用以下 JVM 参数："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/performance-measure.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"`-XX:ActiveProcessorCount` limits how many processors the JVM believes are available, ensuring consistent thread pool sizing across environments.\n"
"`-Xms` and `-Xmx` are set to the same value to eliminate heap resizing during the measurement."
msgstr "`-XX:ActiveProcessorCount` 用于限制 JVM 认为可用的处理器数量，以确保不同环境下的线程池大小保持一致。将 `-Xms` 和 `-Xmx` 设置为相同值，以避免在测量过程中发生堆大小调整。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/performance-measure.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "In the performance lab, CPU affinity is further controlled using `taskset` to pin processes to specific cores, preventing interference between the application, database, load generator, and monitoring."
msgstr "在性能实验室中，通过使用 `taskset` 进一步控制 CPU 亲和性，将进程绑定到特定核心，从而防止应用程序、数据库、负载生成器和监控工具之间相互干扰。"

#. type: Title =
#: _versions/main/guides/performance-measure.adoc
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "Additional flags applied by Quarkus"
msgstr "Quarkus 应用的其他标志"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/performance-measure.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "When Quarkus invokes GraalVM `native-image` it will apply some additional flags by default."
msgstr "当 Quarkus 调用 GraalVM 的 `native-image` 时，它会默认应用一些额外的参数。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/performance-measure.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "You might want to know about the following ones in case you're comparing performance properties with other builds."
msgstr "如果你想将性能特性与其他构建版本进行比较，不妨了解一下以下内容。"

#. type: Title ==
#: _versions/main/guides/performance-measure.adoc
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "Disable fallback images"
msgstr "禁用备用图片"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/performance-measure.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Fallback native images are a feature of GraalVM to \"fall back\" to run your application in the normal JVM, should the compilation\n"
"to native code fail for some reason."
msgstr "备用本机图像（Fallback native images）是 GraalVM 的一项功能，当因某种原因导致编译为本机代码失败时，该功能会“回退”到在普通 JVM 中运行您的应用程序。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/performance-measure.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Quarkus disables this feature by setting `-H:FallbackThreshold=0`: this will ensure you get a compilation failure rather\n"
"risking to not notice that the application is unable to really run in native mode."
msgstr "Quarkus 通过设置 `-H:FallbackThreshold=0` 来禁用此功能：这样可以确保编译失败，从而避免因未察觉应用程序实际上无法以原生模式运行而带来的风险。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/performance-measure.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "If you instead want to just run in Java mode, that's totally possible: just skip the native-image build and run it as a jar."
msgstr "如果你只想以 Java 模式运行，这也是完全可行的：只需跳过 native-image 的构建步骤，直接将其作为 JAR 文件运行即可。"

#. type: Title ==
#: _versions/main/guides/performance-measure.adoc
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "Disable Isolates"
msgstr "禁用隔离项"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/performance-measure.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Isolates are a neat feature of GraalVM, but Quarkus isn't using them at this stage."
msgstr "隔离区是 GraalVM 的一项很棒的功能，但 Quarkus 目前尚未使用该功能。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/performance-measure.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Disable via `-H:-SpawnIsolates`."
msgstr "通过 `-H:-SpawnIsolates` 禁用该功能。"

#. type: Title ==
#: _versions/main/guides/performance-measure.adoc
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "Disable auto-registration of all Service Loader implementations"
msgstr "禁用所有 Service Loader 实现的自动注册"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/performance-measure.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Quarkus extensions can automatically pick the right services they need, while GraalVM's native-image defaults to include\n"
"all services it's able to find on the classpath."
msgstr "Quarkus 扩展可以自动选择所需的服务，而 GraalVM 的原生映像则默认包含其在类路径上能找到的所有服务。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/performance-measure.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "We prefer listing services explicitly as it produces better optimised binaries. Disable it as well by setting `-H:-UseServiceLoaderFeature`."
msgstr "我们更倾向于显式列出服务，因为这样生成的二进制文件优化效果更好。您也可以通过设置 `-H:-UseServiceLoaderFeature` 来禁用此功能。"

