msgstr "如果你想详细调查一些差异，请务必检查 Quarkus 具体调用了什么：当构建插件生成原生映像时，完整的命令行会被记录下来。"

#. type: Title =
#: _versions/main/guides/performance-measure.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Coordinated Omission Problem in Tools"
msgstr "工具中的“协调遗漏”问题"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/performance-measure.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "When measuring performance of a framework like Quarkus the latency experience by users are especially interesting and for that there are many different tools. Unfortunately, many fail to measure the latency correctly and instead fall short and create the Coordinate Omission problem. Meaning tools fails to accommodate for delays to submit new requests when system is under load and aggregate these numbers making the latency and throughput numbers very misleading."
msgstr "在衡量 Quarkus 这类框架的性能时，用户实际感受到的延迟尤为值得关注，为此也有许多不同的工具。 遗憾的是，许多工具无法正确测量延迟，反而存在不足，从而导致“坐标遗漏”问题。这意味着这些工具未能考虑到系统负载较高时提交新请求的延迟，却将这些数据汇总计算，导致延迟和吞吐量数据极具误导性。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/performance-measure.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "A good walkthrough of the issue is https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lJ8ydIuPFeU[this video] where Gil Tene the author of wrk2 explains the issue and https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xdG8b9iDYbE[Quarkus Insights #22] have John O'Hara from Quarkus performance team show how it can show up."
msgstr "关于该问题的详细讲解，可 link:https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lJ8ydIuPFeU[参考这段视频] ：其中，wrk2 的作者 Gil Tene 对此问题进行了说明；此外，在《 link:https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xdG8b9iDYbE[Quarkus Insights》第 22 期中] ，Quarkus 性能团队的 John O’Hara 演示了该问题可能如何表现出来。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/performance-measure.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Although that video and related papers and articles date all back to 2015 then even today you will find tools that fall short with the coordinated omission problem."
msgstr "尽管那段视频及相关论文和文章都可追溯至2015年，但即便是今天，你仍然会发现有些工具在处理“协调性遗漏”问题时仍显不足。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/performance-measure.adoc
#, fuzzy
